review_blob: If you could drink the months of oct and nov this beer is what it would taste like.Seasonal flavors galore, its got a lot goin on. Good stuff.
Solid session beer. Hoppy smell to it. Hoppy after taste but not like an ipa. Calm hops nothing crazy.  Dope session beer if your tired of the cheap stuff.
12 oz. Bottle. Easy to drink. Good session beer. I dont remember flavor notes but just thought it was good.
Not a big IPA fan but I really enjoyed this. I didnt feel like I had a mouthful of hops for hours like I do with most IPAs. Good balance.
